title: Woman and Man Holding Hands: Light Skin Tone, Medium-Dark Skin Tone
description: Depicts a couple, a woman and a man, holding hands. The specific skin tones are represented as light for the woman and medium-dark for the man. It signifies romance, partnership, unity, and connection.
apple_vendor_description: Apple's rendering of the woman and man holding hands emoji showcases a harmonious pairing with a light skin tone for the woman and a medium-dark skin tone for the man, their hands clasped together with gentle, rounded fingers. The smooth gradients and realistic lighting on their skin tones, a hallmark of Apple’s design, suggest unity and companionship. This emoji, seen on Apple devices, conveys partnership, support, and shared experiences, embodying the spirit of connection in a visually appealing and meaningful way.
